uk.ac.qmul.sbcs.evolution.convergence.handlers.documents.parsers.codeml
Class CodemlAncestralGeneralOutputParser

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.qmul.sbcs.evolution.convergence.handlers.documents.parsers.codeml.CodemlAncestralGeneralOutputParser

public class CodemlAncestralGeneralOutputParser
extends java.lang.Object

Class to parse the codeml-anc.out output from the modified codeml-ancestral package by Jason De Koning at evolutionarygenomics.com / U Colorado, and used in Castoe et al. (2009)'s paper on convergence in agamid lizards.

Constructor should be called with a single File argument, this being the location of the codeml-anc.out file. The constructor will then parse the taxon list and phylogeny information from the file.

Note that the branch-pair convergent/divergent site probabilities comparison info is pulled from convergentSites.out by CodemlAncestralSiteOutputParser

Author:
Joe Parker, Kitson Consulting / Queen Mary University of London
See Also:
